  <description type="morphology">Plants rigid. Stems to 10(–15) cm, branches to 15(–30) mm; axillary hair apical cell obtuse, pale brown. Stem leaves broadly rounded to apex, 1.4–2.2 × 1–1.4 mm; base broadly rounded to insertion; alar region small, of 2–4 × 4–6 cells; laminal cells (30–)40–55(–70) × 5–7 µm; basal cell walls incrassate, strongly porose. Seta 1.3–2.3 cm. Capsule 1.5 mm. Spores smooth.</description>
